******************************************************************************
* UTK Robotics 2015-2016                                                     *
* README: QR Code Reader Utility                                             *
******************************************************************************

This utility reads an image from the webcam and processes it for QR codes.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Required Libraries
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This utility requires a few libraries in order to compile.

 - ZBar library with C++ headers
 - OpenCV library with C++ headers and Video4Linux support

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Compilation Directions
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Just run the makefile on a Linux machine.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Running Instructions
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
./read_img

Note about OpenCV... Please ensure that you run the following command:
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:/usr/local/lib

This allows it to find the appropriate OpenCV libraries at runtime. 
